19:T461,Internal brochure evidence clearly identifies this as Meril's Dafodil Neo Aortic Valve, a bovine pericardial bioprosthetic heart valve. External tier1 manufacturer sources confirm: (1) it is a bioprosthetic tissue heart valve for cardiac surgery, (2) features pericardial construction with hemodynamic advantages, (3) designed for both conventional and minimally invasive aortic valve replacement. The Triad frame design with Elgiloy alloy wireform, size range 17-29mm tissue annulus diameter, MRI conditional status at 1.5T/3.0T, and anti-calcification treatment are all consistent with modern surgical bioprosthetic valve technology. Product family classification is appropriate as it represents a sized range (17-29mm) of the same valve platform. Brand field should be populated with 'Meril Life Sciences' but this is administrative cleanup, not semantic conflict. The current title 'Dafodil Neo Aortic Valve' is clinically accurate but enriched title specifies bioprosthetic nature for clarity. Anatomy scope is aortic position only (not mitral/tricuspid). No conflicts detected between internal and external sources.15:["$","$L18",null,{"product":{"product_name":"Meril Dafodil Neo Aortic Valve","product_name_display":"Dafodil Neo Aortic Valve","sku_code":"DDLN-A","product_family":"Dafodil Neo Heart Valves","product_family_display":"Dafodil Neo Heart Valves","slug":"meril-dafodil-neo-aortic-valve","images":[{"id":"75c237653347","storage_path":"agile-ortho/products/69c3ed722a7174181a7c3ebe/cover_e8f48584.jpg","original_filename":"cover_Dafodil-Neo-BROCHUREpdf.pdf.jpg","content_type":"image/jpeg","size":779572,"uploaded_at":"2026-03-26T05:55:39.392021+00:00","source":"brochure_extraction","width":4961,"height":2339},{"id":"0a709bbb585a","storage_path":"agile-ortho/products/69c3ed722a7174181a7c3ebe/cover_1c6cb40b.jpg","original_filename":"cover_Dafodil-Neo-BROCHUREpdf.pdf.jpg","content_type":"image/jpeg","size":779572,"uploaded_at":"2026-03-26T06:00:39.587204+00:00","source"